    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone prioritizing mechanical reliability over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are in good working order, providing a smooth ride for your daily commute. However, the exterior shows its age with some paint fading on the hood and a few minor scratches along the doors. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining consistent with regular use over the years. It is a solid, functional car that has been maintained mechanically but lacks the polish of a newer model.",
