    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior luster and an interior environment that retains its original integrity. Meticulously curated and maintained to the highest standards, it offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking a vehicle that transcends the typical secondary market. Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence in a form that remains as striking today as the day it first departed the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
